<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Jesus makes sure to inform us about the Holy Spirit we will receive before sending us out to share the Gospel.</li></ul></body></html>